like":1063,"dislike":6,"score":1057,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T18:13:08.000Z","msg":"跟輩份嘅<br />\n嘴巴 鼻哥 耳仔 眼精"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad796d08200e1bb559e928a2de62c0c177deba71","tid":542691,"uid":68215,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"《廣州語本字》第三百六十九條有一句<br />\n「衝住鼻齃頭直行」 <br />\n齃者，同頞，鼻樑也。<br />\n「齃」及後被俗稱成「齃若哥」。<br />\n漸演成「鼻哥」"},{"pid":"e44a4e3b9ee2b7363dad46050e36e4fe646ff327","tid":542691,"uid":68215,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《廣州語本字》第三百六十九條有一句<br />\n「衝住鼻齃頭直行」 <br />\n齃者，同頞，鼻樑也。<br />\n「齃」及後被俗稱成「齃若哥」。<br />\n漸演成「鼻哥」</blockquote><br />\n但《廣雅》對「俗讀齃若哥」欠解釋，因此無從得知源頭。<br />\n齃及頞，讀音壓(aat3)"},{"pid":"1652c87b8161f64ef2ea21cacd85e0784c1956c8","tid":542691,"uid":68215,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"至於膝頭哥者，與鼻哥不同<br />\n《廣韻》﹕「髁﹐膝骨。」 《說文》﹕「髀骨也。」 <br />\n另有「䯊」：《廣韻．平聲．歌韻》﹕「膝骨。」 <br />\n兩者皆指膝骨，「膝頭髁」、「膝頭䯊」。我要再查一查先知邊個係正解。<br />\n但係鼻哥同膝頭哥嘅解釋係唔一樣。"},{"pid":"0e682cd6884ae1312bccd169cf22af4aae929356","tid":542691,"uid":68215,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T03:51:03.000Z","msg":"雖然鼻膝解釋唔同，但兩者泛指骨骼，前者鼻樑，後者膝骨。眼睛無骨，因此眼哥不通。"},{"pid":"f723148945fd8cbf707b55de1572f208f93d6783","tid":542691,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee85c3f1d84d62d3a98effd19ca2b1df1921eac","tid":542691,"uid":155404,"like":127,"dislike":8,"score":119,"quote":{"pid":"ddac68afc8736a72276eac62d24861b9a82bbcf7","tid":542691,"uid":104249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:14:55.000Z","msg":"嘴唔會叫嘴哥<br />\n乳頭唔會叫lin哥<br />\n就連膝頭哥個朋友手肘都唔會叫做肘哥<br />\n點解呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.g